  "description": "An out-of-bounds access vulnerability was found in the Linux kernel’s netfilter subsystem. The code path for creating new netfilter tables through `nf_tables_newtable` is missing appropriate safeguards against invalid nf_tables family values. Manipulating these values to allows for memory access beyond the intended boundaries.",
